    <title>Malnutrition contributor: Sam Mednick</title>
    <description>Sam Mednick is a freelance journalist and the Associated Press correspondent in South Sudan. Over the past 13 years, she’s reported on conflict, post-conflict and development stories from the Middle East, Africa, Asia and Europe. Sam writes for VICE, Foreign Policy, Devex and iPolitics, among other international publications. She also produces and hosts a podcast. Follow her work at sammednick.com and on Twitter @sammednick.
</description>
